獩字的汉语字典释义

[①]［huì］

见“獩”。

獩字的康熙字典解释

【巳集下】【犬字部】　獩； 康熙笔画：17； 页码：页719第27
【廣韻】於廢切【集韻】烏廢切，?音穢。【廣韻】本作濊，濊貊，夫餘國名。或作䫉。【集韻】通作薉穢。○按《廣韻》《集韻》《類篇》俱書作獩。

[Siji 2] [Dog Character Department] 　獩; Kangxi strokes: 17; Page number: page 719 27
[Guang Yun] Yu Feiqi [Ji Yun] Wu Feiqie, sound foul. [Guang Yun] This is the name of the country of sip, sip, and husband. Or as a servant. 【Jiyun】Through for stubbornness. ○According to "Guang Yun", "Ji Yun" and "Like Pian" all books are used as a roe.
